headline: Where Will Take-Two Stock Be in 3 Years?
summary: Buzz is building for the next release in the Grand Theft Auto series -- one of the bestselling video game franchises of all time.  Wall Street analysts project Take-Two's adjusted revenue to hit $9 billion in two years.  Shares of Take-Two Interactive (NASDAQ: TTWO) have been trending higher over the past year.
